{"pageid":110203,"pagename":"Shield (weapon)","title":"Shield (weapon)","displaytitle":"Shield (weapon)","revid":14240281,"redirects":["Shield (weapon"],"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"description","value":"Shields are normally a piece of equipment used to defend. However, certain shields can be used to attack or wielded in the weapon slot."}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\">This article is about shields used as weapons. For shields used for defending, see <a href=\"/w/Shields\" title=\"Shields\">Shields</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-header\">Shield</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-image\"><a href=\"/w/File:Dinh%27s_bulwark.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Dinh&#39;s bulwark.png\" src=\"/images/Dinh%27s_bulwark.png?2c9d4\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"27\" height=\"29\" data-file-width=\"27\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\">Primary <a href=\"/w/Attack_type\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Attack type\">type</a></th><td colspan=\"13\"><a href=\"/w/Crush\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Crush\">Crush</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\">Secondary <a href=\"/w/Attack_type\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Attack type\">type</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">N/A</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\"><a href=\"/w/Monster_attack_speed\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Monster attack speed\">Attack speed</a></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-full-width-content\"><a href=\"/w/Attack_speed\" title=\"Attack speed\"><img alt=\"Monster attack speed 5.png\" src=\"/images/Monster_attack_speed_5.png?cf852\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"164\" height=\"46\" data-file-width=\"164\" data-file-height=\"46\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<p><b>Shields</b> are normally a piece of <a href=\"/w/Equipment\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Equipment\">equipment</a> used to <a href=\"/w/Defence\" title=\"Defence\">defend</a>. However, certain shields can be used to attack or wielded in the <a href=\"/w/Weapon_slot\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Weapon slot\">weapon slot</a>.\n</p><p>Most of the shields that can be used to attack are wielded in the <a href=\"/w/Shield_slot\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Shield slot\">shield slot</a> and use a chargeable <a href=\"/w/Special_attack\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Special attack\">special attack</a> to deal damage. The only shield that can be wielded in the weapon slot is <a href=\"/w/Dinh%27s_bulwark\" title=\"Dinh&#39;s bulwark\">Dinh's bulwark</a>.\n</p><p>All of these shields give far more <a href=\"/w/Defence_bonus\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Defence bonus\">defence bonuses</a> than <a href=\"/w/Attack_bonus\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Attack bonus\">attack bonuses</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Combat_styles\">Combat styles</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Shield_(weapon)?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Combat styles\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Shield_(weapon)?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Combat styles\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\"><tbody><tr class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></tr><tr><th><a href=\"/w/Combat_Options\" title=\"Combat Options\">Category</a>: <a href=\"/w/Weapons/Types#Bulwark\" title=\"Weapons/Types\">Bulwark</a></th><th>Combat Style</th><th><a href=\"/w/Attack_types\" title=\"Attack types\">Style type</a></th><th><a href=\"/w/Combat_Options#Melee_weapons\" title=\"Combat Options\">Weapon Style</a></th><th><a href=\"/w/Experience\" title=\"Experience\">Experience</a></th><th><a href=\"/w/Combat_Options#Melee_weapons\" title=\"Combat Options\">Invisible Boost</a></th></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/w/Weapons/Types\" title=\"Weapons/Types\"><img alt=\"CombatStyles Bulwark.png\" src=\"/images/CombatStyles_Bulwark.png?c1217\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"47\" data-file-width=\"150\" data-file-height=\"47\" /></a></td><td>Pummel</td><td>Crush</td><td>Accurate</td><td><a href=\"/w/Attack\" title=\"Attack\">Attack</a> and <a href=\"/w/Hitpoints\" title=\"Hitpoints\">Hitpoints</a></td><td>+3 <a href=\"/w/Attack\" title=\"Attack\">Attack</a></td></tr><tr><td>Block</td><td>None</td><td>None</td><td>None</td><td>None</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/w/File:Operating_dragonfire_ward.gif\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/Operating_dragonfire_ward.gif/200px-Operating_dragonfire_ward.gif?a2148\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/Operating_dragonfire_ward.gif?a2148 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"300\" data-file-height=\"300\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/w/File:Operating_dragonfire_ward.gif\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A player operating a charged dragonfire ward.</div></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Wieldable_shield_weapons\">Wieldable shield weapons</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Shield_(weapon)?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Wieldable shield weapons\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Shield_(weapon)?action=edit&am