rossbow_(weapon)\" title=\"Crossbow (weapon)\">Crossbow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Ballista\" title=\"Ballista\">Ballista</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\"><a href=\"/w/Weapons#Thrown_weapons\" title=\"Weapons\">Thrown</a></td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Dart\" title=\"Dart\">Dart</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Throwing_knife\" title=\"Throwing knife\">Throwing knife</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Throwing_axe\" title=\"Throwing axe\">Throwing axe</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Chinchompa_(weapon)\" title=\"Chinchompa (weapon)\">Chinchompa</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Other</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Defender\" title=\"Defender\">Defender</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Salamander\" title=\"Salamander\">Salamander</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shield</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Fun_weapons\" title=\"Fun weapons\">Fun weapons</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mediawiki‐7bfb498f95‐qlz7t\nCached time: 20220517010602\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.135 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.227 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 221/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 23736/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 82/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.069/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1568651/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  160.362      1 -total\n 72.82%  116.770      2 Template:Infotable_Bonuses\n  9.53%   15.285      1 Template:Weapon\n  8.03%   12.873      3 Template:Navbox\n  7.92%   12.701      1 Template:Otheruses\n  6.91%   11.074      1 Template:Hatnote\n  6.33%   10.148      1 Template:Infobox_Weapon_Group\n  3.06%    4.906      1 Template:CombatStyles\n  2.19%    3.515      1 Template:Ctg\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:110203-0!canonical and timestamp 20220517010602 and revision id 14240281. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{Otheruses|shields used as weapons|shields used for defending|Shields}}\n{{Infobox Weapon Group\n|name = Shield\n|images = [[File:Dinh's bulwark.png]]\n|primary = [[Crush]]\n|secondary = N/A\n|speed = 5\n}}\n'''Shields''' are normally a piece of [[equipment]] used to [[Defence|defend]]. However, certain shields can be used to attack or wielded in the [[weapon slot]].\n\nMost of the shields that can be used to attack are wielded in the [[shield slot]] and use a chargeable [[special attack]] to deal damage. The only shield that can be wielded in the weapon slot is [[Dinh's bulwark]].\n\nAll of these shields give far more [[defence bonus]]es than [[attack bonus]]es.\n\n==Combat styles==\n{{CombatStyles|Bulwark}}\n[[File:Operating dragonfire ward.gif|thumb|200px|A player operating a charged dragonfire ward.]]\n\n==Wieldable shield weapons==\n{{Infotable Bonuses|Dinh's bulwark|sort=acrush|nototals=yes}}\n\n==Non-wieldable shield weapons==\n{{Infotable Bonuses|Ancient wyvern shield#Charged|Dragonfire shield#Charged|Dragonfire ward#Charged|sort=acrush|nototals=yes}}\n\nAside from Dinh's bulwark, all other shields that can do damage can only do so via their [[special attacks]]. All of these special attacks require the shield to be charged.\n\n:''For details, see [[Special attacks#Shields]].''\n\n{{Weapon}}"}